          <h2 style="
              font-size: 22px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 30px !important;
            ">Wolfspeed Secures $1.5B for Expansion</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">Wolfspeed, a chipmaker for electric vehicles, is set to <a href="https://www.bnnbloomberg.ca/business/company-news/2024/10/15/wolfspeed-wins-15-billion-in-financing-from-chips-act-apollo/" target="_blank">receive</a> $750M in U.S. government grants and $750M from Apollo Global Management and other investors. This funding, part of the Chips Act, will help Wolfspeed expand factories in North Carolina and New York, creating over 5,000 jobs. Despite challenges from production issues and wafer shortages, Wolfspeed is hopeful this boost will drive future success. The company’s stock jumped 23% after the announcement, offering some relief after a tough year, with shares down 74% through 2024.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <!-- Content sections -->
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
