        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 500"> Apollo Eyes UK Nuclear Plant Investment</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">Apollo Global Management is in talks to <a href="https://www.bnnbloomberg.ca/investing/2024/10/15/apollo-in-talks-to-partly-finance-edfs-hinkley-uk-nuclear-power-plant/" target="_blank">finance</a> EDF’s Hinkley Point C nuclear plant in the UK. EDF is seeking £4 billion to complete the project, which has been delayed and is now expected to be operational by 2030. Apollo’s potential investment could include both equity and debt as EDF looks for partners to share the rising costs, which have ballooned to nearly £48 billion. With big infrastructure projects facing labor shortages and delays, this deal could be a critical step for the UK’s nuclear ambitions.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <!-- Content sections -->
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
