        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 500"> Selwood Pressures RWE on Buybacks </h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">Activist investor Selwood Asset Management is <a href="https://www.hedgeweek.com/activist-selwood-wants-clarity-on-rwe-share-buyback-plans/#:~:text=Activist%20investor%20Selwood%20Asset%20Management,to%20a%20report%20by%20Bloomberg." target="_blank">urging</a> RWE to clarify its stance on a potential share buyback. RWE’s stock has dropped 23% this year, leaving investors frustrated. Selwood’s Karim Moussalem wrote to the company asking for a clear decision on buybacks, which could boost shareholder value. RWE had hinted at a buyback earlier, but later backtracked.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
