        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 500"> Permutable AI Launches New Trading Tool</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">Permutable AI just <a href="https://www.hedgeweek.com/permutable-ai-launches-trading-co-pilot-for-commodity-markets/" target="_blank">launched</a> Trading Co-Pilot, an AI-driven tool for commodity markets. Designed for traders, the Co-Pilot offers real-time analysis of global news, prices, and sentiment across precious metals and agriculture. It provides buy/sell signals and market insights from 25,000 sources daily, helping traders make faster decisions in volatile markets. The tool plans to expand into stocks and crypto soon, giving traders even more coverage.</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
